@AntiMarketingTO Our tickets always include hand baggage, Brett. The number of items you can carry for free depends on the ticket and destination. Yours should be:

- 1 piece of baggage up to 10 kg / 22 Ibs // 55x40x20cm / 22x16x8in
+ 1 personal item up to 2 kg / 4.4 lb // 40x30x15cm / 16x12x5in

